{"tid":1656681,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"前線手足入 有野想講","createTime":"2019-10-15T17:09:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T17:26:43.000Z","uid":307200,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4aa4decb6ec0c31727ebbf58ed9c74890a620f30","tid":1656681,"uid":307200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:09:13.000Z","msg":"我想講既野就係....<br />\n<br />\n多謝你勇敢無懼<br />\n多謝你無私付出<br />\n多謝你寧死不屈<br />\n多謝你保護我地<br />\n多謝你作為前線<br />\n多謝你從未退下<br />\n多謝你體諒我地<br />\n<br />\n你我素未謀面 你地既付出卻比我地多很多<br />\n如果當初唔係有你地 我地呢一刻可能已經送左中<br />\n<br />\n作為一個最盡去到工兵既和理非<br />\n我本人做到既野唔多 <br />\n但願係未來嘅日子<br />\n每一位手足都要平平安安<br />\n<br />\n最後我好想比一個擁抱比你地<br />\n同埋<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">多謝你</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"7d5f142837657e89bc572b5728fe7e50b6746b49","tid":1656681,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:09:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MHn4YGm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMHn4YGm.jpg&h=a9bf801a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3aa33651765d066c66e3f6f97cad989743b56535","tid":1656681,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:12:33.000Z","msg":"【簡易文宣】本土國際戰線&mdash;Facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656652\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656652</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"edd3445cc963e063307a606a49db8ca01c8e7ee3","tid":1656681,"uid":26952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:26:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/36uGjB5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F36uGjB5.jpg&h=9d83ffec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dxhdaJL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdxhdaJL.jpg&h=e5c0d53a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8e4OJ3M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https: